    # tm "He's a good boss, I guess?"
    tm "他是个好老板，吧？"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:15
translate chinese suzytammys1_efd55374:

    # ss "He's kind of weird though."
    ss "不过他有点怪怪的。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:17
translate chinese suzytammys1_57910419:

    # tm "Oh, he's not that weird."
    tm "哦，他也没那么怪。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:19
translate chinese suzytammys1_2ad68341:

    # pc "What do you mean, weird?"
    pc "你说怪是什么意思？"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:20
translate chinese suzytammys1_f5500674:

    # ss "Like overly cheerful and wholesome."
    ss "就是那种过度开朗又正经的人。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:22
translate chinese suzytammys1_8140ae26:

    # ss "People like that freak me out. Makes me feel like he's hiding something."
    ss "这种人让我毛骨悚然。总觉得他有什么事瞒着我。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:23
translate chinese suzytammys1_15026317:

    # ss "Like he's a secret pervert or something."
    ss "就像他是个隐藏的变态之类的。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:25
translate chinese suzytammys1_3af8aacf:

    # pc "You may be onto something there."
    pc "你可能说对了。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:27
translate chinese suzytammys1_84f23d86:

    # ss "I knew it!"
    ss "我就知道！"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:28
translate chinese suzytammys1_754b07cd:

    # tm "What are you talking about? What do you know?"
    tm "你在说什么？你知道什么？"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:29
translate chinese suzytammys1_6d3f5bbb:

    # pc "I can't say any more!"
    pc "我不能再说了！"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:31
translate chinese suzytammys1_e3b699f1:

    # tm "Really!?"
    tm "真的吗！？"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:32
translate chinese suzytammys1_ef763d54:

    # ss "You're going to do that to us?"
    ss "你要这样对我们？"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:33
translate chinese suzytammys1_4465b574:

    # pc "I'm sorry. I promised!"
    pc "对不起。我答应过！"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:35
translate chinese suzytammys1_0c8828b4:

    # pc "He's not so bad though. It's nothing to worry about."
    pc "不过他其实没那么坏。没什么好担心的。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:37
translate chinese suzytammys1_4570994a:

    # ss "We're going to get it out of you eventually."
    ss "我们迟早会逼你说的。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:38
translate chinese suzytammys1_9d64452a:

    # pc "You think so?"
    pc "你这么认为吗？"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:40
translate chinese suzytammys1_a3419192:

    # tm "We have our ways."
    tm "我们自有办法。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:43
translate chinese suzytammys1_f59ffb5b:

    # tm "I think everybody's a secret pervert... unless they're a pervert openly, anyways."
    tm "我觉得每个人都是个隐藏的变态……除非他们是公开的变态，反正。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:45
translate chinese suzytammys1_2c076b6b:

    # ss "You know those serial killer shows, when the neighbors and co-workers are all like \"He always seemed so nice and normal?\""
    ss "你知道那些连环杀手剧吗，邻居和同事们总是说“他看起来一直那么友善正常？”"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:46
translate chinese suzytammys1_073efbf9:

    # ss "That's what he makes me think of."
    ss "他让我联想到那种感觉。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:48
translate chinese suzytammys1_a4339d9b:

    # tm "Oh come on! He's not a serial killer!"
    tm "哦，别开玩笑了！他不是连环杀手！"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:49
translate chinese suzytammys1_ac8f4b6e:

    # pc "Yeah, damn. I hope it's not anything like that."
    pc "是啊，真他妈的。希望不是那种事。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:51
translate chinese suzytammys1_7939d1e1:

    # ss "I'm sure it's not. But he's hiding something!"
    ss "我确定不是。但他肯定在隐瞒什么！"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:52
translate chinese suzytammys1_d8c3a717:

    # pc "Has he ever done anything weird to you?"
    pc "他有没有对你做过什么奇怪的事？"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:54
translate chinese suzytammys1_7b7ff333:

    # ss "Oh no, nothing like that."
    ss "哦没有，没那种事。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:56
translate chinese suzytammys1_500ad5d2:

    # tm "Yeah me either. Though I'm not completely opposed..."
    tm "是啊，我也没有。虽然我倒也不是完全反对……"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:57
translate chinese suzytammys1_0cfcd499:

    # ss "What!?"
    ss "什么！？"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:59
translate chinese suzytammys1_c996820d:

    # tm "What can I say, he's got that thick daddy vibe."
    tm "我还能说什么呢，他身上有那种粗犷的“老爹”气质。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyTammyConversations/suzytammys1.rpy:60
translate chinese suzytammys1_f070c890:

    # ss "You're such a slut!"
    ss "你真是个荡妇！"

